title: Greatest NFL Feuds
itunes:title: Greatest NFL Feuds
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, & Colleen Wolfe – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including the Jets cutting David Harris, the Chiefs releasing Jeremy Maclin, and Dennis Pitta re-injuring his hip. The heroes also preview the Miko Grimes vs Gregg Rosenthal twitter beef before diving into their favorite NFL feuds from over the years.
